Raz mkstat
Call TEXTE(22321,GBOUT1) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(47277,GBOUT2) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(6028,GBOUTS) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(12276,GBOUTP) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUTA) From OBJDIV
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_POT(zc) From W1CTR1
Onkey 130 Titled GBOUT2 Call B2_POT(zc) From W1CTR1
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_POT(zc) From W1CTR1
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_POT(zc) From W1CTR1
Onkey 146 Titled GBOUTA Call SA_POT(zc) From W1CTR1
Gosub _AFF
End

Subprog C_POT(VALEUR)
